Class TableManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • tablr.TableManager

  • public class TableManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Responsibility:
    Manage the tables and the current table.
    Invariants:
  • there are never 2 table with the same name in the tables.
        for each x,y in getTableNames():
           if x != y:
               !x.equals(y)
  • no table is ever null
        for i in 0...getNbTables():
           getTableAt(i) != null
